OL,3,CMother of 12-year-old boy rioter on
OL,4,Choliday in Ibiza while he attended
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FA judge has ordered the mother of a 12-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy involved in the summer
OL,9,Friots to appear alongside him after
OL,10,Fhearing she had flown to Ibiza instead
OL,11,Fof being with her son in court.
OL,13,FDistrict Judge Joanne Hirst told
OL,14,FManchester Magistrates' Court she was
OL,15,F"frankly astonished" that the boy's
OL,16,Fmother was abroad on a five-day
OL,17,Fsunshine break, as he admitted two
OL,18,Fcounts of violent disorder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
