OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FJudge Hirst adjourned sentencing of
OL,8,Fthe boy, who is too young to be named,
OL,9,Fand ordered a parental summons so the
OL,10,Fmother must appear before the court to
OL,11,Fexplain her actions.
OL,13,FThe boy was accompanied to court by
OL,14,Fhis uncle and had earlier admitted
OL,15,Fbeing part of a mob that attacked a
OL,16,Fbus outside a hotel housing asylum
OL,17,Fseekers in Manchester on 31 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
