OL,3,CMother of 12-year-old boy rioter on
OL,4,Choliday in Ibiza while he attended
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"I will require a full explanation
OL,8,Ffrom mum on her decision to go on
OL,9,Fholiday one day before her 12-year-old
OL,10,Fson comes to court facing a potential
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,13,F"This is a serious situation, it has
OL,14,Fnow deteriorated in my view because of
OL,15,Fthe actions of the mother. She is on
OL,16,Fnotice - I will be challenging her
OL,17,Fabout this decision."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
