OL,3,CMother of 12-year-old boy rioter on
OL,4,Choliday in Ibiza while he attended
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FAddressing the boy as she adjourned
OL,8,Fsentencing to September 11, Judge
OL,9,FHirst told him: "Boys like you need
OL,10,Ftheir mums in their lives. I need your
OL,11,Fmum here."
OL,13,FIn a separate hearing in the same
OL,14,Fcourt, a 16-year-old boy was told he
OL,15,Fwas being given "the biggest chance in
OL,16,Fyour life" by Judge Hirst, who decided
OL,17,Fto pass a referral order rather than
OL,18,Fjail the youngster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
