OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1725306726
OL,3,CMother of 12-year-old boy rioter on
OL,4,Choliday in Ibiza while he attended
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe teenager, accompanied by his
OL,8,Fmother, had admitted violent disorder
OL,9,Fby throwing a bottle at a police horse
OL,10,Fduring widescale trouble in Bolton
OL,11,Ftown centre last month.
OL,13,FThe court heard the youngster's father
OL,14,Fhad died and his mother, who
OL,15,Faccompanied him to court, was having
OL,16,Ftreatment for cancer.
OL,18,FHe was asked by the judge: "What were
OL,19,Fyou thinking?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
