OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1725306726
OL,3,CMother of 12-year-old boy rioter on
OL,4,Choliday in Ibiza while he attended
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe boy replied: "I was not really
OL,8,Fthinking anything. We came into town
OL,9,Fand everything just erupted.
OL,10,FAdrenaline. I'm disgusted with myself."
OL,12,FThe youngster's mother told the court:
OL,13,F"He's frightened to death of going to
OL,14,Fprison. I think this has been a
OL,15,Fmassive wake-up call."
OL,17,FThe judge warned the youngster he had
OL,18,Fnarrowly avoided custody and instead
OL,19,Fgave him a 12-month referral order
OL,20,Fwith intensive supervision and a
OL,21,Fcurfew.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
